data.description: *ASSUMABLE 3.625% FIXED VA INTERST RATE!* Subject to VA Eligibility. Incredible (price per square foot) VALUE for this 2,697 sf, 3 Bedrm, 2.5 Bath Brick Colonial Style Home in a Great Neighborhood! INTERIOR Features inc: Formal Living & Dining Rms, Spacious Kitchen, Large Breakfast/Keeping Rm Area, Sliding Barn Doors that separate a HUGE Family Room with Built-in Bookshelves & Cabinetry, Downstairs Master, Office, and 2 Upstairs Bedrms with a Loft/Study Area. Hardwood Flooring throughout the Formal areas & in ALL Bedrooms. Heavy Ceramic & Brick Tile Flooring in the Kitchen, Breakfast/Keeping Area, Family Room & Baths. Wood burning Fireplace, Extensive Molding & Woodwork, and much more! EXTERIOR Features inc: Mostly Brick Siding, Large 20x6 Back Porch, 20x14 Detached Wired Storage Building that could be used as a small WORKSHOP & 14x8 Covered Shelter. Option: There is an Adjoining Fenced .24 Acre Lot immediately behind this property For Sale for an additional $55,000. See MLS#2537686.
